<h2>Keyboard</h2>
<h3>Hex Keypad</h3>
<p>
Default 2 hex keypads are supported. The second keypad is configured when 'VP580 Expansion Keypad' or the 'VP590 Colour Board' is selected. The only known game using 2 keypads is the Chip-8X game blockout.
</p>
<p>
To change and view the hex keypad to PC key mapping select the 'Key Map' button, see also chapter <a href="KeyMappingMain.htm">Key Mapping</a>
</p>
<h3>Keyboard</h3>
<p>
To use the VIP with ASCII keyboard support select the keyboard checkbox. 
</p>
</BODY>
